{% comment %}
Edge Timer - App Embed Block

This app embed loads the urgency timer assets and initialization context globally.
Merchants can enable/disable it in:

  Theme editor → Theme settings → App embeds

Once enabled, your urgency-timer.js script will:
- Mount product timers on pages where the product-timer block is placed
- Mount top/bottom bar timers on any page according to your app's configuration

This replaces the need for merchants to manually add snippets to theme.liquid.
{% endcomment %}

{%- comment -%}
Load the timer CSS and JS assets globally
{%- endcomment -%}
<meta name="shopify-shop" content="{{ shop.permanent_domain }}">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ 'urgency-timer.css' | asset_url }}" media="all">
<script src="{{ 'urgency-timer.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{%- comment -%}
Provide a hidden bar context so top/bottom bars can mount on any page,
even when no product timer block is present.
{%- endcomment -%}
<div
  id="urgency-timer-bar-context"
  class="urgency-timer-context"
  data-shop-domain="{{ shop.permanent_domain }}"
  style="display: none;"
>
  <!-- Hidden context element for bar timers to ensure shop detection works -->
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Edge Timer",
  "target": "head",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Enable this to load the Edge Timer script on all pages. This allows product countdown timers and promotional bars to display where configured in your Edge Timer app dashboard."
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
